%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^ORANGE%^Earth Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The earth domain pulls solely from the power of elemental
earth.  Some of its spells alter the caster, while others
may do damage to foes.

Clerics with the Earth Domain gain the following benefits:
- Acid resistance equal to their cleric level.
- %^GREEN%^Acid Dart%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The earth domain contains the following spells:

Soften Earth, Strength of Stone, Earth Reaver, Wall of Stone, Earthquake

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nimnavanon, Nilith

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
